	zoom20sv
	zoomec


Wizard
------
This is a demonstration of the Wizard product.

Downloaded to:
	ICLAS2/SYS:\

To run:
	boot your PC using the "Wizard/BA Boot Disk" that Morgan Fletcher
		can give you.
	login as MRDEMO, DEMOJR, or DEMOSR.


